            <div1 id="BQ-41-4-0007">
                <head>
                    <title type="section">CORRIGENDUM</title>
                </head>
                <p>In my note on Benjamin Blake, the landscape artist whom the Royal Academy exhibition
catalogue of 1808 mistakenly credits with <hi rend="i">The Vision of the Last Judgment</hi> 
(<hi rend="i">Blake</hi> 41.3 [winter 2007-08]: 135), I wrote that this mistake has been silently corrected by
scholars. G. E. Bentley, Jr., notes that it is explicitly corrected in his <hi rend="i">Blake Records</hi>,
2nd ed., 250fn. —</p>
                <byline>
                    <docAuthor>Morton D. <name>Paley</name>
                    </docAuthor>
                </byline>
            </div1>
